Fhome&d=2fXvMHh%2FMpctJjSDIpTO%2B9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=2643f90f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.singaporeair.com/zh_TW/hk/home</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">泰航 TG</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thaiairways.com/zh_HK/index.page\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiairways.com%2Fzh_HK%2Findex.page&d=2fXvMHh%2FMpctJjSDIpTO%2B9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=27c41fbb\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.thaiairways.com/zh_HK/index.page</a><br />\n<br />\n想claim保險去隔離post問<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/257722/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/257722/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟個人心得:<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">UO專區</span></span><br />\n根據過往經驗<br />\n佢情願cancel都唔會delay<br />\n自己執生<br />\n如果買咗保險 記得拎延遲證明書<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">CX專區</span></span><br />\n如果你喺日本同韓國返香港<br />\n如果你真係非一定要如期返香港不可嘅話<br />\n你打去CS問下可唔可以改經台北返香港先<br />\n台北返香港班次多好多<br />\nDelay影響會較小"},{"pid":"a2cce9d77c9e2144d82da7f16deb2a360f641604","tid":383430,"uid":5475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T13:08:51.000Z","msg":"原本諗住買機票星期日飛高雄<br />\n而家搞到我好唔好DELAY多一日先飛..."},{"pid":"3c9175b5480339b0be2ee3ec7707db238a6dcb92","tid":383430,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T13:15:12.000Z","msg":"星期日下午高雄飛返來點睇？"},{"pid":"338cfab13da0a58d47019f4f1cb257d4d36ae602","tid":383430,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T13:16:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>星期日下午高雄飛返來點睇？</blockquote><br />\nKA"},{"pid":"fdf816dcbc17ea939db0ba818941ad38cd2421ee","tid":383430,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T13:19:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">KA</span></span><br />\n<br />\n熱帶風暴瑪娃影響往來香港航班<br />\n最後更新: 2017年9月1日 14:00 HKT (GMT+8)<br />\n<br />\n我們正密切監測颱風瑪娃對航班運作的影響。目前航班運作維持正常，但隨著瑪娃逐漸迫近香港，<span style=\"color: red;\">我們預料2017年9月3日（星期日）的抵港及離港航班將受延誤。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">國泰航空／國泰港龍航空由即時起豁免涉及香港機票之重新訂位及更改航點費用</span>，詳情請參閱有關熱帶風暴瑪娃之特別票務安排。我們建議乘客如在允許的情況下更改行程。<a href=\"http://如您透過cathaypacific.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%A6%82%E6%82%A8%E9%80%8F%E9%81%8Ecathaypacific.com&d=2fXvMHh%2FMpctJjSDIpTO%2B9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=80dbd884\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">如您透過cathaypacific.com</a>及手機應用程式訂票，您可使用自助訂位管理服務查更改預訂；或聯絡您的旅行代理提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n請瀏覽航班延誤及取消(只提供英文版)了解航班受影響時的服務恢復安排。"},{"pid":"ae7d1e7dd30a95dae1b0167a370e9146a768f6be","tid":383430,"uid":126348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T13:22:07.000Z","msg":"星期一朝早台中回香港 UO 點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bcf7be09938d860822b6069d99d2979aceed9f0","tid":383430,"uid":3864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T13:27:16.000Z","msg":"3號星期日夜晚10點飛土耳其<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2186dd2e8003ba40ca10016baa84be5058ccee50","tid":383430,"uid":39511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T13:29:00.000Z","msg":"星期日朝飛台北<br />\n<br />\n改唔改機票好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c143461ca70503bcff66be3b40a5003788ee54","tid":383430,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T13:32:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3號星期日夜晚10點飛土耳其<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9649e822ed624d2e28648e9c78b5e0c5a24f0131","tid":383430,"uid":562